  "kind": "Definition",
  "title": "Pointwise Maximum of Two Functions",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $X\\subseteq\\mathbb{R}$ and let $f,g:X\\to\\mathbb{R}$. The\npointwise maximum $\\max(f,g):X\\to\\mathbb{R}$ is the function defined by\n\\[\n \\max(f,g)(x)=\\max\\{f(x),g(x)\\}\n \\qquad (x\\in X).\n\\]",
